---
// HomeCardGrid.astro
---

<div class="home-card-grid">
  <a class="home-card home-card--dark home-card--large" href="/knowledge/">
    <div class="home-card-topline">
      <span>01 / KNOWLEDGE</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="home-card-label">知识专题</p>
      <h3>理解原理，<br />也理解边界。</h3>
      <p>按稳定的技术领域，组织经过整理和验证的长期知识。</p>
    </div>
  </a>

  <a class="home-card home-card--soft" href="/learning-paths/">
    <div class="home-card-topline">
      <span>02 / PATHS</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="home-card-label">学习路线</p>
      <h3>从一篇笔记，<br />走向完整能力。</h3>
      <p>明确目标、前置知识与阅读顺序，让学习不再随机发生。</p>
    </div>
  </a>

  <a class="home-card home-card--blue" href="/retrospectives/">
    <div class="home-card-topline">
      <span>03 / RETROSPECTIVES</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="home-card-label">问题复盘</p>
      <h3>结论很重要。<br />抵达结论的过程更重要。</h3>
      <p>完整保留现象、排查、根因、方案与验证，让经验真正可复用。</p>
    </div>
  </a>
</div>
